## ğŸ§ Audio System

- ExoPlayer used for streaming and local playback.
- Equalizer applied using `audioSessionId`.
- User EQ settings stored and reapplied dynamically.
- Supports:
  - Band Level Control
  - Bass Boost
  - Preset Switching
  - Live EQ refresh without restarting playback

